00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:08,500
エンドロールは終わらない
Endroll Never Ends

3
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:08,500
作詞・作曲：瀬名航
Lyrics/Composition: Wataru Sena

4
00:03:09,112 --> 00:03:11,178
扉の向こう繋いで
Connecting beyond the door,

5
00:03:11,178 --> 00:03:13,750
生まれたはずの世界は
the world that was supposed to be born...

6
00:03:14,321 --> 00:03:17,345
思いよりずっと難しくて
Is much harder than I thought,

7
00:03:17,345 --> 00:03:20,100
夢がこぼれてた
and my dreams were spilling out.

8
00:03:21,045 --> 00:03:23,901
伝えたいことなんて
Because there aren't many things

9
00:03:23,901 --> 00:03:26,540
いくつもありはしないから
I want to say,

10
00:03:27,521 --> 00:03:30,342
儚く脆い僕の声は
my fleeting and fragile voice

11
00:03:30,342 --> 00:03:32,855
かすれてゆきそうだ
seems to be fading away.

12
00:03:33,312 --> 00:03:35,789
三度目のなんとかだって
Even for the third time or whatever,

13
00:03:35,789 --> 00:03:38,211
続ける意味を探して
searching for the meaning to continue,

14
00:03:39,012 --> 00:03:41,220
未開拓だった旅の先
ahead of the unexplored journey,

15
00:03:41,220 --> 00:03:42,511
これでいいと
saying "this is fine",

16
00:03:43,045 --> 00:03:46,512
よかったとそう言えるまで
until I can say "I'm glad I did it".

17
00:03:50,812 --> 00:03:53,211
このまま終われば誰かの美談として
If it ends like this, will it be

18
00:03:53,211 --> 00:03:55,621
消費されていくでしょうか
consumed as someone's beautiful story?

19
00:03:56,812 --> 00:03:59,211
ずっと後悔ばかり思い出す日々を
Now is the time to laugh,

20
00:03:59,211 --> 00:04:02,045
背負って笑う今だ
carrying the days of remembering only regrets.

21
00:04:02,512 --> 00:04:05,451
そんな悲しい顔をしないできっと
Don't make such a sad face,

22
00:04:05,451 --> 00:04:08,511
間違ってないから
I'm sure it's not a mistake.

23
00:04:09,211 --> 00:04:12,311
間違いになんて絶対に
I will never

24
00:04:12,311 --> 00:04:14,545
しないよ
let it become a mistake.

25
00:04:20,512 --> 00:04:23,511
すれ違いのひとつふたつだって
I spent my time trying not to care

26
00:04:23,511 --> 00:04:26,545
気にしないように過ごしてた
about one or two misunderstandings.

27
00:04:27,012 --> 00:04:29,541
哀さの宿ったこの身体
Because I loved this body

28
00:04:29,541 --> 00:04:32,045
愛してたから
where sadness dwelt.

29
00:04:33,012 --> 00:04:35,311
何者にもなれなくて
Along with the time I spent struggling

30
00:04:35,311 --> 00:04:37,045
もがき続けた時間ごと
because I couldn't become anyone,

31
00:04:38,012 --> 00:04:40,441
肯定できるか分からない
I don't know if I can affirm it,

32
00:04:40,441 --> 00:04:43,045
分からないけど
I don't know, but...

33
00:04:44,212 --> 00:04:46,611
辛ければ辛いほど
The harder it is,

34
00:04:46,611 --> 00:04:49,045
笑い話にもなるでしょう
the more it will become a funny story, right?

35
00:04:50,012 --> 00:04:53,011
君の声だって聞こえるから
Because I can hear your voice too,

36
00:04:53,512 --> 00:04:55,845
大丈夫だよ　大丈夫だよ
It's okay, it's okay.

37
00:04:55,912 --> 00:04:59,011
最高な日も　最悪な日も
On the best days, and the worst days too,

38
00:05:00,033 --> 00:05:04,233
いざ三千里 これが生き様だと呼べるなら
If I can call this way of life a journey of three thousand miles...

39
00:05:04,433 --> 00:05:09,133
目的地なんてない 僕らは生きている
There's no destination, but we are alive.

40
00:05:09,633 --> 00:05:11,833
何度願い 何度滲み
How many times have I wished, how many times have I wept,

41
00:05:11,833 --> 00:05:15,333
何度怒り 何度嘘をついてしまったんだ
how many times have I been angry, and how many times have I lied?

42
00:05:15,833 --> 00:05:18,233
こんな見窄らしくて 恥ずかしくて
So shabby and shameful...

43
00:05:18,233 --> 00:05:21,433
真面目すぎる僕を 隠さずに晒すよ
I'll expose my overly serious self without hiding.

44
00:05:21,833 --> 00:05:25,033
ずっと誰にも言えないこの気持ちを
These feelings I've never been able to tell anyone...

45
00:05:25,033 --> 00:05:28,033
吐き出してしまいたい
I want to spit them all out.

46
00:05:28,433 --> 00:05:32,433
君を傷つけてしまって
I ended up hurting you.

47
00:05:32,733 --> 00:05:36,433
初めて夢を描いた時から
Since the time I first envisioned a dream,

48
00:05:36,433 --> 00:05:39,033
もう何年経った？
how many years have passed?

49
00:05:39,433 --> 00:05:44,233
気づいたらみんな いなくなっていた
Before I knew it, everyone was gone.

50
00:05:44,733 --> 00:05:50,333
僕らは出会いと別れを繰り返していく
We keep repeating encounters and partings.

51
00:05:50,833 --> 00:05:56,633
ただ時間が過ぎて 終わりが来る
Time simply passes, and the end comes.

52
00:05:57,133 --> 00:06:02,333
これでいい 後悔は後は自分で決めるだけだ
This is fine. I'll decide my regrets for myself.

53
00:06:02,833 --> 00:06:08,033
綺麗で歪な想い出を歌にしよう
Let's turn beautiful and distorted memories into a song.

54
00:06:08,533 --> 00:06:14,033
何回でも そう何回でも届けよう
No matter how many times, yes, no matter how many times, I'll deliver it.

55
00:06:39,133 --> 00:06:41,033
嗚呼...
Ah...

56
00:06:40,833 --> 00:06:43,433
藍彩 - Aisai - / AZKi

57
00:06:41,333 --> 00:06:44,833
指をすり抜けて
Slipping through my fingers...

58
00:06:43,433 --> 00:06:45,433
作詞・作曲・編曲：Keeno
Lyrics, Music, Arrangement: Keeno

59
00:06:45,333 --> 00:06:51,133
やっと君を閉じ込めたのに
Even though I finally managed to lock you away.

60
00:06:51,633 --> 00:06:58,233
繰り返してる呼吸に混ざって
Mixing with my repetitive breaths,

61
00:06:58,733 --> 00:07:04,433
少しずつ零れてしまいそうで
it feels like it's about to spill out bit by bit.

62
00:07:04,933 --> 00:07:12,233
いっそこのまま 誰にも届かない
I'd rather just, as I am now, unreachable by anyone,

63
00:07:12,733 --> 00:07:18,933
深い夜の底で息を止めて
hold my breath at the bottom of the deep night...

64
00:07:19,433 --> 00:07:21,533
しまいたい
...and end it all.

65
00:07:22,033 --> 00:07:27,933
どくん、どくんと 涙の代わりに
Thump, thump... instead of tears,

66
00:07:28,433 --> 00:07:34,833
悲しくなるほど 音立てる心臓
my heart beats so loudly it makes me sad.

67
00:07:35,333 --> 00:07:41,433
分かっているの 分かっているのだけど
I know. I know, but...

68
00:07:41,933 --> 00:07:48,333
まだこんなにも 君をただこんなにも
still so much, I just, so much for you...

69
00:07:59,233 --> 00:08:05,133
口を噤んで 膝を抱えて
With my mouth shut, holding my knees,

70
00:08:05,633 --> 00:08:11,933
そろそろ泣いてもいいですか
is it okay if I cry soon?

71
00:08:12,433 --> 00:08:18,533
繰り返す幕の 行き着く先まで
Until the very end of these repeating acts,

72
00:08:19,033 --> 00:08:25,033
私の全部に君がいた
you were in everything of mine.

73
00:08:25,533 --> 00:08:31,433
もう二度と君に 触れられないこんな
If this is a body that can never...

74
00:08:31,933 --> 00:08:33,433
身体なら意味はなくて
...touch you again, it has no meaning.

75
00:08:33,433 --> 00:08:38,133
今すぐにでも脱ぎ捨てて
I want to cast it off right now...

76
00:08:38,633 --> 00:08:40,433
しまいたいのに
...and be done with it, but...

77
00:08:40,433 --> 00:08:42,533
もがいてもどうしようもなくて
no matter how I struggle, it's hopeless.

78
00:08:43,033 --> 00:08:50,533
酷く膿んだこの傷を 掻き毟っている
I'm scratching at this terribly festered wound.

79
00:08:51,033 --> 00:08:57,433
いっそこのまま 私にはいらない
I'd rather just, as I am now, I don't need it.

80
00:08:57,933 --> 00:09:03,933
暗い夜の底で息をしてる
I'm breathing at the bottom of the dark night.

81
00:09:04,433 --> 00:09:10,033
明日なんて このまま泣いて
Forget about tomorrow; if I just keep crying like this...

82
00:09:10,533 --> 00:09:16,133
全部溢れたら 君を知らない
...and everything overflows, will I be able to become...

83
00:09:16,633 --> 00:09:18,933
私になれるのかな
...a version of myself that doesn't know you?

84
00:09:19,433 --> 00:09:25,633
どくん、どくんと 涙が枯れても
Thump, thump... even if my tears run dry,

85
00:09:26,133 --> 00:09:32,133
この身体中を 巡る焼けるような赤
this burning red circulates through my body.

86
00:09:32,633 --> 00:09:38,133
分かっているの 分かっているのだけど
I know. I know, but...

87
00:09:38,633 --> 00:09:44,533
これじゃあまりにも この恋があまりにも
This is just too much. This love is just too much.

88
00:09:45,033 --> 00:09:51,533
まだこんなにも 君をただこんなにも
Still so much, I just, so much for you...

89
